00:31:13.783 --> 00:31:17.116
Cherry. Dođi pomoći s
mamom. Vrijeme je da krenemo.

00:32:30.860 --> 00:32:32.860
Tko je?

00:32:40.620 --> 00:32:42.620
Nat?

00:32:47.126 --> 00:32:49.126
Što to radiš?

00:32:58.346 --> 00:33:00.473
Trebao sam to prije napraviti.

00:33:02.892 --> 00:33:04.892
Došao si ovamo da me poljubiš?

00:33:11.317 --> 00:33:13.695
Ne, ne, ne.

00:33:16.489 --> 00:33:18.866
Nemam puno.

00:33:19.325 --> 00:33:23.246
Svoju vjeru, mamu, baku.

00:33:23.496 --> 00:33:26.499
Dosad mi je to bilo dovoljno.

00:33:28.501 --> 00:33:31.879
Cherry, bila bi mi prava
čast da budeš moja supruga.

00:33:31.921 --> 00:33:36.467
Bio bih dobar prema tebi.
Životom bih te čuvao.

00:33:36.718 --> 00:33:38.718
Ako me uzimaš.

00:33:40.722 --> 00:33:43.641
Da. Da, uzimam.

00:33:58.531 --> 00:34:00.531
Što sada?

00:34:01.951 --> 00:34:04.151
Razgovarat ću o tome sa Samuelom.

00:34:04.328 --> 00:34:07.081
Srediti nam kolibu za vaše posjete.

00:34:07.832 --> 00:34:09.959
U redu.

